{"tid":2270471,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"共和黨代表顏色要轉黑色呀 用乜撚野紅色","createTime":"2020-11-04T04:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T13:01:44.000Z","uid":25754,"like":22,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d4db08450df246de8c32af6ba539c02c164a66","tid":2270471,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:57:35.000Z","msg":"我唔撚係話浸浸係condom,想唔想佢地贏，支唔支持。<br />\n我淨係講一樣野，浸浸呢鑊輸左，你地以後著個件就係中國香港市波衫，<br />\n諗下呢三個月受過既苦受過既難，<br />\n你仲可唔可以心安理得咁著住件紅色既狗皮？<br />\n大紫荊旗個隻紅色啊！"},{"pid":"2c86f6a6abac3cf0e8cd8ef1b9b037f295cbd87a","tid":2270471,"uid":74569,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"你邊撚個呀"},{"pid":"9855bbb2dbf3ba6a888ef0bc816e229dcadf90db","tid":2270471,"uid":218659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"大陸紅 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc59ab056483fed3e0c7852a4f3ee4f57efe73f6","tid":2270471,"uid":218659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2c86f6a6abac3cf0e8cd8ef1b9b037f295cbd87a","tid":2270471,"uid":74569,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T04:59:49.000Z","msg":"你邊撚個呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:31:21.000Z","msg":"香港而家辦緊喪，仲用紅色<br />\n做香港人真係陰鳩公"},{"pid":"b533be02721c5df08777267fd2c4c11a12f92281","tid":2270471,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:33:38.000Z","msg":"係 唔轉色就係食人血饅頭 手足唔好去美國"},{"pid":"0968d12d59e3a30d4ccdc7b601e0d8549b86741f","tid":2270471,"uid":263991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"經典重溫<br />\n<br />\n<em>著黑衫入場睇港隊啊，乜撚野紅衫啊？</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1556608\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1556608</a>"},{"pid":"7f515296fa7c569579c3f2077c9f5365c512a8db","tid":2270471,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"本來一開始話唔同派別放低對立，共抗土共，唔知幾時開始變晒撐共和黨，仲要著紅色衫<